title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2011 Jan 11 TU [sebaygo1]

The Peter Schiff Show
Tuesday, 11 January 2011


[sebaygo1]


Tonight's show will be hosted by Andrew Schiff with guest Allan Mansoor, Republican California assemblyman & member of the budget committee, on why Republicans are objecting to Gov. Brown's proposed cuts in the state budget. Later in the show, Dan Carlin, host of "Hardcore History," will join us to discuss whether the creeping wussification of America means our best days are behind us.
